race.comment: TROIKA (7) wasn't too far off them in Saturday metro grade at the latest effort and will find this task a touch easier. Hoop Thornton sticks following that last-start outing and should be right there when the whips are cracking. EN POINTE (4) has a win and a placing from two attempts over this course and distance and will strip fitter second-up from the break. Rates highly on best figures. LAYDOWNLILY (8) is a bit hit or miss but is more than capable enough on her day. Is a four-time winner here and look for sharp improvement. SHALAILED (6) is one from one around this circuit and will be rock-hard fit for this. Top-three aspirations. RISE OF THE MASSES (2) rounds out the selections.
